{
  "stem": "10818.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when I came out of the-- And-- and at the same time, I should say, with the knowledge that it was probably not going to be possible for Jewish children to attend the public schools, a Jewish district school had been formed.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There had always been an old orthodox Jewish school, because there was an old orthodox community.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I-- there was no thought-- was ever given to my going there, because it was orthodox.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Even though I know some of the people who were in it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and-- but at the time, in 1934, they formed this new school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the staff of the new school consisted of teachers, Jewish teachers, who had been let go by the municipal schools, by the-- the public schools, who were no longer allowed to teach there.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Consequently-- and they were brilliant teachers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Consequently, this school was organized to take all grades.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, you know, it was large enough to-- to have-- you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were enough children to have a substantial school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And fortunately, there was also a space for it, near the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The-- the synagogue, which had been built in 1912, had-- had some extra rooms for meeting rooms and so on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So there was space for it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we had a very nice school with excellent teachers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I-- ?] I must come back for a minute.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "When I came out of that exam, and my parents realized what they put me through unnecessarily, they said, you're not going to go there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You're going to the Jewish district school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I went there and had my teachers became lifelong friends.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The-- my fellow students are lifelong friends.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We were a small community and we were not allowed to be in touch with anybody outside.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
